School Faculty =
School Faculty members include any teachers, professors, principals, and deans. It will display their first and last name, gender, job title, age, sexuality (if known), relationship status (if known), and nationality (if they were from a different [[Nations|nation]] than the one your character is currently from. It will also show their four teacher stats: Relationship, Looks, Strictness, and Popularity.
